\c 3
\s Inkulumo kaMozisi iyaqhubeka
\p
\v 1 Sasesiphenduka sisenyuka ngendlela yeBashani. UOgi inkosi yeBashani wasephuma ukumelana lathi, yena labantu bakhe bonke\x + Nani 21.33. Dute. 29.7.\x*, ukulwa eEdreyi\x + 3.10. Dute. 1.4.\x*.
\v 2 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kimi: Ungamesabi, ngoba ngizamnikela labantu bakhe bonke lelizwe lakhe esandleni sakho; njalo uzakwenza kuye njengokwenza kwakho kuSihoni inkosi yamaAmori owayehlala eHeshiboni\x + Nani 21.24,34.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu yanikela esandleni sethu loOgi inkosi yeBashani labo bonke abantu bakhe; sasesimtshaya, kakwaze kwasala lansali kuye\x + Nani 21.33,35.\x*.
\v 4 Sasesithumba yonke imizi yakhe ngalesosikhathi; kwakungelamuzi esingawuthathanga kibo; imizi engamatshumi ayisithupha, isabelo sonke seArigobi, umbuso kaOgi eBashani\x + 3.13,14. 1 Kho. 4.13.\x*.
\v 5 Yonke limizi yayivikelwe ngemithangala ephakemeyo, amasango lemigoqo, ngaphandle kwemizana eminengi kakhulu engelamithangala\x + 1 Sam. 6.18. Esta 9.19.\x*.
\v 6 Sasesiyitshabalalisa\x + 7.2.\x*, njengokwenza kwethu kuSihoni inkosi yeHeshiboni\x + 2.24. Nani 32.37.\x*, satshabalalisa yonke imizi, abesilisa labesifazana labantwanyana\x + 2.34.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa zonke izifuyo lempango yemizi, saziphangela.
\v 8 Ngalesosikhathi sasesithatha esandleni samakhosi amabili amaAmori ilizwe, elalinganeno kweJordani, kusukela esifuleni iArinoni kuze kube sentabeni yeHermoni.
\v 9 (AmaSidoni ayibiza iHermoni\x + 4.48. Josh. 11.3,17. 12.1,5. 13.5,11. Hlab. 42.6. 89.12? 133.3. Ngoma 4.8.\x* ngokuthi yiSiriyoni\x + Hlab. 29.6. Dute. 4.48.\x*, lamaAmori ayibiza ngokuthi yiSeniri\x + 1 Lan. 5.23. Ngoma 4.8.\x*.)
\v 10 Yonke imizi yemagcekeni, leGileyadi yonke, leBashani yonke\x + 4.43. Josh. 13.9,16,17,21.\x*, kuze kube seSaleka leEdreyi\x + Josh. 12.5. 13.11.\x*, imizi yombuso kaOgi eBashani.
\v 11 Ngoba nguOgi kuphela, inkosi yeBashani, owasalayo kunsali yeziqhwaga\x + 3.13. 2.11,20. Josh. 12.4. 13.12. Gen. 14.5. Amos 2.9.\x*; khangela, umbheda wakhe wawungumbheda wensimbi; kawukho yini eRaba yabantwana bakoAmoni\x + 2 Sam. 11.1. 12.26. Jer. 49.2. Hez. 21.20. 25.5. Amos 1.14. Josh. 13.25.\x*? Ubude bawo babuzingalo eziyisificamunwemunye, lobubanzi bawo babuzingalo ezine, ngokwengalo yomuntu\x + Isam. 21.17.\x*.
\v 12 Lalelilizwe sadla ilifa lalo ngalesosikhathi; kusukela eAroweri, elisesifuleni seArinoni, lengxenye yentaba yeGileyadi\x + 2.36.\x* lemizi yayo ngayipha abakoRubeni labakoGadi\x + Nani 32.33. Josh. 12.6. 13.8.\x*.
\v 13 Lokuseleyo kweGileyadi leBashani yonke, umbuso kaOgi, ngakunika kungxenye yesizwe sakoManase\x + Nani 32.29. Josh. 13.29-31.\x*; isabelo sonke seArigobi, layo yonke iBashani\x + Dute. 3.4,14.\x*, eyayithiwa yilizwe leziqhwaga\x + 3.11.\x*.
\v 14 UJayiri indodana kaManase wathatha isabelo sonke seArigobi\x + Nani 32.41.\x*, kuze kube semngceleni wamaGeshuri lowamaMahakathi; wayibiza imizi ngebizo lakhe\x + Josh. 12.5. 13.11,13. 1 Sam. 27.8. 2 Sam. 3.3. 10.6. 13.37,38.\x* \add wathi\add* yiBashani-Havothi-Jayiri, kuze kube yilolusuku\x + Nani 32.41.\x*.
\v 15 Ngasengimnika uMakiri iGileyadi\x + Nani 32.39.\x*.
\v 16 LakwabakoRubeni lakwabakoGadi nganika kusukela eGileyadi ngitsho kuze kufike esifuleni seArinoni, phakathi laphakathi kwesifula, lomngcele, njalo kuze kube sesifuleni iJaboki\x + 2 Sam. 24.5.\x*, umngcele wabantwana bakoAmoni\x + Nani 21.24. Josh. 12.2.\x*.
\v 17 Lamagceke, leJordani, lomngcele, kusukela eKinerethi\x + Nani 34.11.\x* njalo kuze kufike elwandle lwemagcekeni\x + 4.49.\x*, ulwandle lwetshwayi\x + Gen. 14.3.\x*, ngaphansi kweAshidodi-Pisiga ngasempumalanga.
\p
\v 18 Ngasengililaya ngalesosikhathi ngisithi: IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ilinikile lelilizwe libe yilifa lenu. Lizachapha lihlomile phambi kwabafowenu, abantwana bakoIsrayeli, wonke amadodana angamaqhawe\x + Nani 32.21.\x*.
\v 19 Kuphela omkenu labantwanyana benu lezifuyo zenu - ngiyazi ukuthi lilezifuyo ezinengi - kuzahlala emizini yenu engilinike yona\x + Nani 32.1,4.\x*,
\v 20 iN\nd kosi\nd* ize ibanike ukuphumula abafowenu njengani, baze bathi labo badle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ebaphe lona, ngaphetsheya kweJordani\x + Josh. 22.4.\x*; beselibuyela, ngulowo lalowo elifeni lakhe, engilinike lona.
\p
\v 21 Njalo ngamlaya uJoshuwa ngalesosikhathi ngisithi: Amehlo akho abonile konke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ekwenze kulawomakhosi amabili\x + Nani 27.18.\x*; izakwenza njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* kuyo yonke imibuso ozakwedlulela kuyo.
\v 22 Lingabesabi, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, yona izalilwela\x + Eks. 14.14.\x*.
\v 23 Ngasengiyincenga iN\nd kosi\nd* ngalesosikhathi ngisithi:
\v 24 Nkosi Jehova, wena usuqalile ukutshengisa inceku yakho ubukhulu bakho lesandla sakho esilamandla\x + 5.24. 11.2. 32.3. 1 Lan. 29.11.\x*; ngoba nguwuphi unkulunkulu emazulwini lemhlabeni ongenza njengemisebenzi yakho lanjengamandla akho\x + Eks. 15.11.\x*?
\v 25 Ngicela ngichaphe, ngibone ilizwe elihle elingaphetsheya kweJordani, leyontaba enhle\x + Eks. 3.8; Dute. 4.22.\x*, leLebhanoni\x + Josh. 1.4.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yangithukuthelela ngenxa yenu, kayingizwanga\x + Hlab. 78.21,59. 89.38. Dute. 1.37.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Kwenele kuwe; ungabe usaphinda ukukhuluma kimi ngaloludaba\x + 2 Kor. 12.9.\x*.
\v 27 Yenyukela engqongeni yePisiga\x + Nani 27.12,13.\x*, uphakamisele amehlo akho ngentshonalanga langenyakatho langeningizimu langempumalanga, ukhangele ngamehlo akho; ngoba kawuyikuchapha le iJordani.
\v 28 Kodwa laya uJoshuwa\x + Nani 27.23. Dute. 1.38. 31.3,7.\x*, umkhuthaze\x + 1.38. 31.7.\x*, umqinise\x + 2.30. 31.7.\x*; ngoba yena uzachapha phambi kwalababantu, laye abenze badle ilifa lelizwe ozalibona\x + 1.38. 31.7.\x*.
\v 29 Sasesihlala esigodini maqondana leBeti-Peyori\x + 4.46. 34.6.\x*.
